The chunks are slices and do not overlap. If `chunk_size` does not divide the length of the slice, then the last chunk will not have length `chunk_size`.

See [`rchunks_exact`](about:blank/primitive.slice.html#method.rchunks_exact "method slice::rchunks_exact") for a variant of this iterator that returns chunks of always exactly `chunk_size` elements, and [`chunks`](about:blank/primitive.slice.html#method.chunks "method slice::chunks") for the same iterator but starting at the beginning of the slice.

