Convert a vector into a boxed slice.

Before doing the conversion, this method discards excess capacity like [`Vec::shrink_to_fit`](about:blank/vec/struct.Vec.html#method.shrink_to_fit "method std::vec::Vec::shrink_to_fit").

##### [§](#examples-137)Examples

```
assert_eq!(Box::from(vec![1, 2, 3]), vec![1, 2, 3].into_boxed_slice());
```

[Run](https://play.rust-lang.org/?code=%23!%5Ballow(unused)%5D%0Afn+main()+%7B%0A++++assert_eq!(Box::from(vec!%5B1,+2,+3%5D),+vec!%5B1,+2,+3%5D.into_boxed_slice());%0A%7D&edition=2021)

Any excess capacity is removed:

```
